Design Rationale:
- Typography: Combines 'Sporting Grotesque' (a modern, slightly quirky sans-serif) for headings with 'Newsreader' (a sophisticated serif) for body text
- Color Palette: Earthy greens and cream, reflecting farm and nature
- Texture: Subtle grid background suggesting field lines, soft gradients
- Layout: Intentionally asymmetric, with organic typography and border treatments
- Subtle Animations & Hover States: Gradient text underlines, soft shadows

The design communicates sustainability through:
- Organic color palette
- Careful typography choices
- Textural background suggesting agricultural patterns
- Explicit sourcing note
- Elegant, considered layout that feels crafted, not mass-produced

